od.oracle.apps.xxom.atp
Class ATPRecordType

java.lang.Object
  od.oracle.apps.xxom.atp.ATPRecordType

public class ATPRecordType
extends java.lang.Object

Object type of the ATP inquiry. Consists of all the input attibutes, derived attributes and output attributes. Provides get and set Methods for setting and retrieving the data.
